    <h1>Help & Support</h1>
    <p>Welcome to <b>Safarsathi!</b> Find answers to common questions and learn how to make the most of our platform.</p>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>1. Getting Started</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Sign up for a Safarsathi account using your email or social media login.</li>
            <li>Verify your email to access all features of the platform.</li>
            <li>Complete your profile to enhance credibility and improve your experience.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>2. Hosting a Listing</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Navigate to the "Host a Listing" section and provide details about your property or service.</li>
            <li>Upload high-quality images to attract potential guests.</li>
            <li>Set pricing, availability, and any specific conditions for your listing.</li>
            <li>Once approved, your listing will be visible to users searching for stays or services.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>3. Writing & Managing Reviews</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Users can review hosts and listings based on their experience.</li>
            <li>Be honest and constructive when writing reviews.</li>
            <li>Authenticated users can edit or delete their own reviews anytime.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>4. Privacy & Security</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Your personal information is protected and will not be shared with unauthorized third parties.</li>
            <li>Secure authentication is used to prevent unauthorized access to accounts.</li>
            <!-- <li>Report suspicious activity through the "Contact Support" section.</li> -->
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>5. Troubleshooting & Support</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>If you encounter technical issues, try clearing your browser cache and cookies.</li>
            <li>For account-related concerns, visit the "Account Settings" page.</li>
            <li>Contact our support team at <mark>'"trivikramagroupofltd@gmail.com"'</mark> for further assistance.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>6. Terms & Conditions</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Review our <a href="/privacy">Terms & Conditions</a> to understand your rights and responsibilities.</li>
            <li>Ensure your listings and reviews comply with Safarsathi's policies.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Need Further Assistance?</h2>
    <p>If you have additional questions or require support, reach out to us via email or our contact form. We're here to help!</p>

